  * Support renaming music file.
  * Imporve GStreamer working backend.
  * Improve the database reading and write performance.
  * Improve the album view widget rendering performance.
  * Improve the language files searching under Linux.
  * Fixed the debian package doesn't contains language file bug.
  * Fixed the GStreamer duration bug.
  * Removed Phonon and MPV backend[Abandon].
  * Removed JSON database.

